1278
00:40:03.679 --> 00:40:05.679 position:50.00%,start align:start size:27.14% line:73.96% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>You can't</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1279
00:40:03.679 --> 00:40:05.679 position:50.00%,start align:start size:40.48% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>possibly believe</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1280
00:40:03.679 --> 00:40:05.679 position:50.00%,start align:start size:38.57% line:84.62% 
