1309
00:41:38.170 --> 00:41:39.251 position:38.57%,start align:start size:32.86% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Your choice.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1310
00:41:53.806 --> 00:41:56.846 position:38.57%,start align:start size:51.90% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>There'll be no further</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1311
00:41:53.806 --> 00:41:56.846 position:38.57%,start align:start size:51.90% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>resistance, Commander.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

