00:42:12.201 --> 00:42:13.880 position:19.52%,start align:start size:25.24% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Tahna...</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1313
00:42:13.880 --> 00:42:16.200 position:19.52%,start align:start size:32.86% line:79.29% 
