<c.white><c.mono_sans>One day, you'll understand.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1319
00:42:23.597 --> 00:42:25.557 position:42.38%,start align:start size:25.24% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Traitor.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

